{"type": "article", "id": 21796, "title": "Combo mug by Richard Hutten", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115142peslXAV3DrE68xnm.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">荷兰设计师 Richard Hutten 带来的马克杯有两只对称的“耳朵”，每一只“耳朵”几乎和杯子一样的大小，充满了童趣。设计师称这是为他 2 岁儿子设计的，可以保持喝水的平衡而不让水倾倒出来，他想以此鼓励小孩主动多喝水。杯子只有 9cm 高，采用 PP 塑料，手柄是普通的塑料，可选 7 种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.gispen.com/products/dombo-cup/\">现在可在 Gispen 上购买。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115140hoqAf69rxW5yvR2c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115140C2DRKl341qjiYNUJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115141l1n9a4u7AVevFCfL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021151419BAXGgKfINbij6tH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}